00:26:55.700 --> 00:26:57.010
&gt;&gt; Good morning

00:26:57.010 --> 00:26:58.310
&gt;&gt; Edwidge Danticat: Good morning.

00:26:58.310 --> 00:26:59.610
&gt;&gt; How are you?

00:26:59.610 --> 00:27:00.910 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Edwidge Danticat: Fine thank you.

00:27:00.910 --> 00:27:02.840
&gt;&gt; Good. When my daughter
was in high school,

00:27:02.840 --> 00:27:06.150
